race.comment: OLDPOP (11) is edging closer and looks ready to break through after a strong Halidon effort. Back to 1200m today could be the query, though he's turned in some strong figures in recent efforts. Just needs to be holding his recent form to be knocking this off. SOUL SLIDES AWAY (12) wasn't beaten far on debut and should tighten up nicely second-up. Needs some luck from a tricky gate, but she's expected to be hitting the line hard. SURVEY LANE (5) resumes for the Allen yard and has shown glimpses. Could sneak into the frame in a thin race. HATESCHOOLCONCERTS (10) has been solid without winning and gets her chance to improve again third-up.
